/*!
\page freemat_help HELP Help

<p>
Section: \ref sec_freemat "FreeMat Functions"
\section Usage
Displays help on a function available in FreeMat.  The help function
takes one argument:
\verbatim
  help topic
\endverbatim
where <tt>topic</tt> is the topic to look for help on.  For scripts, the 
result of running <tt>help</tt> is the contents of the comments at the top
of the file.  If FreeMat finds no comments, then it simply displays
the function declaration.
*/
